cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_dtx_threshold to a negative value (-1) will cause invalid L1 layer configuration and PRACH detection issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_dtx_threshold 設定為負值 (-1) 會導致無效的 L1 層配置，並造成 PRACH 檢測問題。
